      "content": "i get that but calling it a \"not suitable replacement\" sounds a bit dramatic lol. i've seen so many people say it works just as well for mild anxiety. i'm just really tired of the side effects from the zoloft. if i just lowered my dose for a few days while i start the st johns wort, wouldnt that be a safer way to transition? just trying to figure out a way to do this myself since my doctor is so hard to reach.",
